# GitHub Linguist: keep the language bar focused on the Python pipeline,
# not the large notebooks and cached data artifacts.
*.ipynb    linguist-documentation

data/**    linguist-generated
results/** linguist-generated
figures/** linguist-generated
*.parquet  linguist-generated
